{"tid":1810404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【成績表】崇光百貨：「遊客紅利」已享受咗！","createTime":"2020-01-04T00:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T06:33:01.000Z","uid":202464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c576fb48b757e1da58bead33e2a15c426b99a05","tid":1810404,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:11:53.000Z","msg":"SOGO財務總監潘福全：<br />\n<br />\n國內遊客帶來的龐大生意額(「遊客紅利」）會慢慢消失，至於消失得有多快和有多深，要視乎未來中港關係和社會事件走勢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSOGO與商戶的租約模式與其他商場不同，基本上不設固定租金，但每月設有「最低營業額要求」，再按營業額繳付租金分成。「因應每月社會狀況，個別月份會waive（豁免）呢個最低營業額要求，舖頭做幾多生意就按返比例交幾多租。又或者係降低個營業額要求」，相比奢侈品牌在其他商場佔用更多舖面面積所需付之固定租金，SOGO的租戶較有彈性"},{"pid":"9b8f8734fe59eac0b1770ae89009c1b68eb2c4d1","tid":1810404,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:33:57.000Z","msg":"用 Word List Highlighter 可更易分辨五毛<br />\n有巴打幫手寫咗個教學點善用我個 list<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aprbdKV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aprbdKV</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/20/bwLpWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F20%2FbwLpWU.png&h=71d928b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">* 本名單已加入會員註冊日期以供參考</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"871f5895f65788b3906f74ae10720a413ad05867","tid":1810404,"uid":269506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"Sogo好撚狗，咁多間百貨最撚仆街就係佢"},{"pid":"445c2b30f3e335a7e183397091b90df9766cf61e","tid":1810404,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bb547fb3312fe1c7f91669eaa609a694f291fc","tid":1810404,"uid":19927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"871f5895f65788b3906f74ae10720a413ad05867","tid":1810404,"uid":269506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"Sogo好撚狗，咁多間百貨最撚仆街就係佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75f1012e19ae38774a0784b05403803a7d51066","tid":1810404,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a8bb547fb3312fe1c7f91669eaa609a694f291fc","tid":1810404,"uid":19927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"871f5895f65788b3906f74ae10720a413ad05867","tid":1810404,"uid":269506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"Sogo好撚狗，咁多間百貨最撚仆街就係佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"崇光香港百貨有限公司（英文：SOGO HONG KONG）是香港的一間百貨公司，原本屬於日本崇光百貨，現時則由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利福國際</span></span>（港交所：1212）持有，財務上已經與日本崇光沒有任何關係，但與日本崇光仍有一定的業務合作。 <br />\n<br />\n利福國際集團有限公司（港交所：1212，英語：Lifestyle International Holdings，簡稱利福國際）是一間香港上市的企業，公司在開曼群島註冊，主席為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉鑾鴻</span></span>。利福國際的主要業務是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">崇光百貨</span></span>和透過附屬<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利福中國</span></span>（港交所：2136持有上海、蘇州、大連久光百貨和上海閘北區312街坊33丘約34.8萬平方米的商業綜合體及石家莊北國人百集團29.4%股權投資 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉鑾鴻</span></span>（英文：Thomas Lau Luen-hung，1953年－），綽號「細劉」，籍貫廣東潮州潮安縣，香港出生，利福國際（港交所：1212）董事總經理[1]，華人置業（港交所：127）主席<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉鑾雄</span></span>的胞弟，少東家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉鳴煒</span></span>的叔叔。[2] <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926666b8dfef60e7bbeabde50331283dbc763409","tid":1810404,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb1a8ba790c9ba2dd8378a4bd1500a2c0dc2933","tid":1810404,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"港資黎 不過大陸好多生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47e0308f8f326a71425967c16c1e0ff555dbd5b","tid":1810404,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"我聽返黎就無減過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0123230cc330ad105e5a65c62c1ea4806586bf9b","tid":1810404,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47e0308f8f326a71425967c16c1e0ff555dbd5b","tid":1810404,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"我聽返黎就無減過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"即係sogo管理層講大話？"},{"pid":"06c2f4de59863a49dd0ed4e8d207a8519fe9d4da","tid":1810404,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0123230cc330ad105e5a65c62c1ea4806586bf9b","tid":1810404,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47e0308f8f326a71425967c16c1e0ff555dbd5b","tid":1810404,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"我聽返黎就無減過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"即係sogo管理層講大話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"咁我又唔敢講<br />\n因為我都係聽返黎<br />\n叫晒d supplier上去傾話減租<br />\n但係最後都係無減到"}]}